    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The reverence, worship, or allegiance accorded individuals identified as saints, often expressed through ceremonies, prayers, or other religious rituals.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
